<!-- ── S7 ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="sec" id="s7">
  <div class="slabel"><span class="tro">07 / Kısa Kodlar &amp; Widget</span><span class="eno">07 / Shortcodes &amp; Widget</span></div>
  <h1 class="h1 tro">Kısa Kodlar &amp; Widget</h1><h1 class="h1 eno">Shortcodes &amp; Widget</h1>

  <h2 class="h2">[erta_booking]</h2>
  <p class="p tro">Rezervasyon widget'ını herhangi bir sayfaya eklemek için:</p>
  <p class="p eno">Add the booking widget to any page or post:</p>
  <div class="sc" onclick="cpText('[erta_booking]',this)">[erta_booking] <span style="color:var(--text3);font-size:13px;margin-left:8px">— click to copy</span></div>
  <table class="tbl">
    <thead><tr><th class="tro">Parametre</th><th class="eno">Parameter</th><th class="tro">Açıklama</th><th class="eno">Description</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><span class="mono">department="ID"</span></td><td class="tro">Belirli departmana önceden yönlendirir, o adımı atlar</td><td class="eno">Pre-selects a department and skips that step</td></tr>
      <tr><td><span class="mono">provider="ID"</span></td><td class="tro">Belirli sağlayıcıya önceden yönlendirir</td><td class="eno">Pre-selects a provider and skips that step</td></tr>
      <tr><td><span class="mono">hide_steps="..."</span></td><td class="tro">Virgülle ayrılmış adımları gizler. Örn: <code class="ci">department,provider</code></td><td class="eno">Hides comma-separated steps. E.g. <code class="ci">department,provider</code></td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h2 class="h2">[erta_my_appointments]</h2>
  <p class="p tro">Giriş yapmış müşterilerin kendi randevularını görüntüleyip yönetmesini sağlar:</p>
  <p class="p eno">Allows logged-in customers to view and manage their own bookings:</p>
  <div class="sc" onclick="cpText('[erta_my_appointments]',this)">[erta_my_appointments] <span style="color:var(--text3);font-size:13px;margin-left:8px">— click to copy</span></div>

  <h2 class="h2 tro">Mode-Bazlı Rezervasyon Akışı</h2><h2 class="h2 eno">Mode-Based Booking Flow</h2>
  <ol class="steps">
    <li><span class="tro">Sistem `general`, `department_no_provider`, `department_with_provider`, `provider_only` modlarından uygun olanı uygular</span><span class="eno">System applies one of: `general`, `department_no_provider`, `department_with_provider`, `provider_only`</span></li>
    <li><span class="tro">Moda göre departman ve/veya sağlayıcı adımı gösterilir</span><span class="eno">Department and/or provider steps are shown based on selected mode</span></li>
    <li><span class="tro">Takvim + müsait slot seçimi yapılır</span><span class="eno">Calendar and available slot selection</span></li>
    <li><span class="tro">Form alanları doldurulur; form bazlı “Booking Button Text” değeri varsa butona uygulanır</span><span class="eno">Form fields are completed; per-form “Booking Button Text” overrides submit label when set</span></li>
    <li><span class="tro">Onay/ödeme (Pro) adımı sonrası uygun kanal(lar)dan bildirim gönderilir</span><span class="eno">After confirmation/payment (Pro), notifications are sent via enabled channel(s)</span></li>
  </ol>
  <div class="call call-info"><span class="call-icon">ℹ</span><div class="call-body"><span class="tro">Personelsiz modlarda slotlar sağlayıcı havuzundan birleştirilir ve seçilen slotun `provider_id` değeri rezervasyonda korunur.</span><span class="eno">In personless modes, slots are aggregated from provider pools and selected slot `provider_id` is preserved at booking time.</span></div></div>
</section>

<!-- ── S8 ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="sec" id="s8">
  <div class="slabel">08 / REST API</div>
  <h1 class="h1">REST API</h1>

  <div class="rgrid" style="grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(220px,1fr))">
    <div class="ritem"><div class="rl">Base URL</div><div class="rv" style="font-size:12px;font-family:var(--mono)">/wp-json/erta/v1/</div></div>
    <div class="ritem"><div class="rl tro">Kimlik Doğrulama</div><div class="rl eno">Auth</div><div class="rv" style="font-size:13px">Application Passwords / JWT</div></div>
    <div class="ritem"><div class="rl tro">Yanıt Formatı</div><div class="rl eno">Response</div><div class="rv">JSON</div></div>
  </div>

  <h2 class="h2 tro">Endpoint Listesi</h2><h2 class="h2 eno">Endpoint Reference</h2>
  <table class="tbl">
    <thead><tr><th>Method</th><th>Endpoint</th><th class="tro">Açıklama</th><th class="eno">Description</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><span class="mget">GET</span></td><td><span class="mono">/departments</span></td><td class="tro">Aktif departmanları listeler</td><td class="eno">List all active departments</td></tr>
      <tr><td><span class="mget">GET</span></td><td><span class="mono">/providers</span></td><td class="tro">Sağlayıcıları listeler (?department_id ile filtreler)</td><td class="eno">List providers, filter with ?department_id</td></tr>
      <tr><td><span class="mget">GET</span></td><td><span class="mono">/availability</span></td><td class="tro">Müsait slotları döner</td><td class="eno">Return available slots for provider &amp; date range</td></tr>
      <tr><td><span class="mpost">POST</span></td><td><span class="mono">/appointments</span></td><td class="tro">Yeni rezervasyon oluşturur</td><td class="eno">Create a new booking</td></tr>
      <tr><td><span class="mget">GET</span></td><td><span class="mono">/appointments/{id}</span></td><td class="tro">Tek rezervasyon detayı</td><td class="eno">Retrieve a single booking</td></tr>
      <tr><td><span class="mpatch">PATCH</span></td><td><span class="mono">/appointments/{id}</span></td><td class="tro">Durumu günceller (admin)</td><td class="eno">Update booking status (admin)</td></tr>
      <tr><td><span class="mdel">DELETE</span></td><td><span class="mono">/appointments/{id}</span></td><td class="tro">Rezervasyonu iptal eder</td><td class="eno">Cancel a booking</td></tr>
      <tr><td><span class="mget">GET</span></td><td><span class="mono">/working-hours</span></td><td class="tro">Çalışma saatlerini döner</td><td class="eno">Return working hours config</td></tr>
      <tr><td><span class="mget">GET</span></td><td><span class="mono">/forms/{id}</span></td><td class="tro">Form alanlarını döner</td><td class="eno">Return form fields</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h2 class="h2 tro">Örnek: Slot Sorgulama</h2><h2 class="h2 eno">Example: Fetching Available Slots</h2>
  <div class="cb"><div class="ch"><div class="dots"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div><span>HTTP Request</span><button class="ccopy" onclick="cpBlock(this)">Copy</button></div>
<pre><span class="kw">GET</span> /wp-json/erta/v1/availability
    ?provider_id=<span class="nm">3</span>
    &amp;date_from=<span class="str">2025-06-01</span>
    &amp;date_to=<span class="str">2025-06-07</span>

<span class="cm">// Response</span>
{
  <span class="str">"2025-06-02"</span>: [<span class="str">"09:00"</span>, <span class="str">"09:30"</span>, <span class="str">"10:00"</span>, <span class="str">"14:00"</span>],
  <span class="str">"2025-06-03"</span>: [<span class="str">"10:30"</span>, <span class="str">"11:00"</span>, <span class="str">"15:00"</span>, <span class="str">"15:30"</span>]
}</pre></div>

  <h2 class="h2 tro">Örnek: Rezervasyon Oluşturma</h2><h2 class="h2 eno">Example: Creating a Booking</h2>
  <div class="cb"><div class="ch"><div class="dots"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div><span>HTTP Request</span><button class="ccopy" onclick="cpBlock(this)">Copy</button></div>
<pre><span class="kw">POST</span> /wp-json/erta/v1/appointments
{
  <span class="str">"provider_id"</span>   : <span class="nm">3</span>,
  <span class="str">"department_id"</span> : <span class="nm">1</span>,
  <span class="str">"start_time"</span>    : <span class="str">"2025-06-02 14:00:00"</span>,
  <span class="str">"customer_name"</span> : <span class="str">"Ahmet Yılmaz"</span>,
  <span class="str">"customer_email"</span>: <span class="str">"ahmet@ornek.com"</span>,
  <span class="str">"customer_phone"</span>: <span class="str">"+90 555 123 4567"</span>,
  <span class="str">"form_data"</span>     : { <span class="str">"notlar"</span>: <span class="str">"İlk muayene"</span> }
}</pre></div>
</section>

<!-- ── S9 ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="sec" id="s9">
  <div class="slabel"><span class="tro">09 / WordPress Hook'ları</span><span class="eno">09 / WordPress Hooks</span></div>
  <h1 class="h1 tro">WordPress Hook'ları</h1><h1 class="h1 eno">WordPress Hooks</h1>

  <h2 class="h2 tro">9.1 Action Hook'ları</h2><h2 class="h2 eno">9.1 Action Hooks</h2>
  <table class="tbl">
    <thead><tr><th>Hook</th><th class="tro">Tür</th><th class="eno">Type</th><th class="tro">Açıklama</th><th class="eno">Description</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><span class="mono">erta_loaded</span></td><td><span class="tag-a">Action</span></td><td class="tro">Eklenti tamamen yüklendiğinde tetiklenir</td><td class="eno">Fires when the plugin is fully loaded</td></tr>
      <tr><td><span class="mono">erta_appointment_created</span></td><td><span class="tag-a">Action</span></td><td class="tro">Yeni rezervasyon oluşturulduğunda</td><td class="eno">Fires when a new booking is created</td></tr>
      <tr><td><span class="mono">erta_appointment_confirmed</span></td><td><span class="tag-a">Action</span></td><td class="tro">Rezervasyon onaylandığında</td><td class="eno">Fires when a booking is confirmed</td></tr>
      <tr><td><span class="mono">erta_appointment_cancelled</span></td><td><span class="tag-a">Action</span></td><td class="tro">Rezervasyon iptal edildiğinde</td><td class="eno">Fires when a booking is cancelled</td></tr>
      <tr><td><span class="mono">erta_appointment_rescheduled</span></td><td><span class="tag-a">Action</span></td><td class="tro">Yeniden planlandığında</td><td class="eno">Fires when a booking is rescheduled</td></tr>
      <tr><td><span class="mono">erta_before_booking_saved</span></td><td><span class="tag-a">Action</span></td><td class="tro">Veritabanına yazılmadan önce</td><td class="eno">Fires before a booking is saved to the DB</td></tr>
      <tr><td><span class="mono">erta_after_booking_saved</span></td><td><span class="tag-a">Action</span></td><td class="tro">Veritabanına yazıldıktan sonra</td><td class="eno">Fires after a booking is saved to the DB</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h2 class="h2 tro">9.2 Filter Hook'ları</h2><h2 class="h2 eno">9.2 Filter Hooks</h2>
  <table class="tbl">
    <thead><tr><th>Hook</th><th class="tro">Tür</th><th class="eno">Type</th><th class="tro">Açıklama</th><th class="eno">Description</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><span class="mono">erta_is_pro_active</span></td><td><span class="tag-f">Filter</span></td><td class="tro">Pro aktif mi? Varsayılan: false</td><td class="eno">Is Pro active? Default: false</td></tr>
      <tr><td><span class="mono">erta_slot_duration</span></td><td><span class="tag-f">Filter</span></td><td class="tro">Slot süresini özelleştirmek için (dk)</td><td class="eno">Customise slot duration (min)</td></tr>
      <tr><td><span class="mono">erta_available_slots</span></td><td><span class="tag-f">Filter</span></td><td class="tro">Hesaplanan slot listesini değiştirmek için</td><td class="eno">Modify the computed slot list</td></tr>
      <tr><td><span class="mono">erta_notification_channels</span></td><td><span class="tag-f">Filter</span></td><td class="tro">Bildirim kanallarını genişletmek için</td><td class="eno">Extend notification channels</td></tr>
      <tr><td><span class="mono">erta_email_headers</span></td><td><span class="tag-f">Filter</span></td><td class="tro">E-posta başlıklarını özelleştirmek için</td><td class="eno">Customise email headers</td></tr>
      <tr><td><span class="mono">erta_booking_form_data</span></td><td><span class="tag-f">Filter</span></td><td class="tro">Form verisini doğrulama/dönüştürme</td><td class="eno">Validate or transform form data</td></tr>
      <tr><td><span class="mono">erta_appointment_status_label</span></td><td><span class="tag-f">Filter</span></td><td class="tro">Durum etiketlerini özelleştirmek için</td><td class="eno">Customise status label strings</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h2 class="h2 tro">9.3 Kod Örnekleri</h2><h2 class="h2 eno">9.3 Code Examples</h2>
  <p class="p tro">Rezervasyon oluşturulduğunda özel mantık çalıştırma:</p>
  <p class="p eno">Run custom logic when a booking is created:</p>
  <div class="cb"><div class="ch"><div class="dots"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div><span>PHP</span><button class="ccopy" onclick="cpBlock(this)">Copy</button></div>
<pre><span class="fn">add_action</span>( <span class="str">'erta_appointment_created'</span>,
    <span class="kw">function</span>( \ErtAppointment\Domain\Appointment\Appointment <span class="rx">$appt</span> ): <span class="kw">void</span> {
        <span class="cm">// CRM entegrasyonu, webhook tetikleme vb. / CRM push, webhook, etc.</span>
        <span class="fn">my_crm_create_contact</span>( <span class="rx">$appt</span>->customerEmail, <span class="rx">$appt</span>->customerName );
    }
);</pre></div>

  <p class="p tro">Belirli sağlayıcı için slotları filtreleme:</p>
  <p class="p eno">Filter available slots for a specific provider:</p>
  <div class="cb"><div class="ch"><div class="dots"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div><span>PHP</span><button class="ccopy" onclick="cpBlock(this)">Copy</button></div>
<pre><span class="fn">add_filter</span>( <span class="str">'erta_available_slots'</span>,
    <span class="kw">function</span>( <span class="kw">array</span> <span class="rx">$slots</span>, <span class="kw">string</span> <span class="rx">$date</span>, <span class="kw">int</span> <span class="rx">$providerId</span> ): <span class="kw">array</span> {
        <span class="kw">if</span> ( <span class="rx">$providerId</span> !== <span class="nm">5</span> ) <span class="kw">return</span> <span class="rx">$slots</span>;
        <span class="cm">// Yalnızca sabah slotları / Morning slots only</span>
        <span class="kw">return</span> <span class="fn">array_filter</span>( <span class="rx">$slots</span>, <span class="fn">fn</span>( <span class="rx">$s</span> ) => <span class="rx">$s</span> &lt; <span class="str">'12:00'</span> );
    },
<span class="nm">10</span>, <span class="nm">3</span> );</pre></div>
</section>

<!-- ── S10 ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
